{"title":"Infecciones de Dispositivos de Drenaje Ventricular-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/Infecciones de Dispositivos de Drenaje Ventricular-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Infecciones de Dispositivos\\Nde Drenaje Ventricular","guid":"apqmQbvhRA7-dm8dz9trvQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Introducción","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Dispositivos de drenaje ventricular","guid":"VFCKgFSU--pG-sUeNNn8CQ","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Extremo proximal ⟶ ventrículo","guid":"Wjtb2J97tjtN-7d_eZH_rQ","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"• Extremo distal:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"• Externalizado (transitorios) ⟶ DVE","guid":"qpZrPe7cfrbjgh7JefoiLA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"• Internalizado (permanentes) ⟶ DVP (derivación peritoneal),\\NDVA (derivación ventrículo-atrial), ventrículo-pleural","guid":"d0FMx3nYQh-5SdeLp_B-jA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"7","parent":"0","text":"• Vías de infección:","guid":"vYy3CKWh1ckaXDOvYaGXTQ","children":[{"id":"8","parent":"7","text":"• Colonización del catéter ⟶ flora de piel al momento de la instalación","guid":"sKeBqtiqU_J9xwx7iJQ4AA","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"7","text":"• Infección retrógrada ⟶ contaminación del extremo distal (cavidad abdominal, peritonitis, perforación) o sistema colector","guid":"p70ymEeLfUjFODc1A-TOFQ","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"7","text":"• Desde la piel ⟶ manipulación posterior o exposición del catéter","guid":"fAX_k9rOk_mChKqkARVKqA","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"7","text":"• Siembra hematógena","guid":"5cwKQUMzbOMSofjhBJ--Bw","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"0","text":"• Tasa de Infección:","guid":"rHB4bl9eCYm4JCGMYOZeYQ","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"• Infecciones de shunt: 5-15%, >60% en el primer mes","guid":"1VWabVhRKc5EzXp0woefdw","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"• Infecciones DVE: 0-22%, generalmente en la primera semana","guid":"M2KJ0Uq6QqMUQnRMBUOtGA","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"xyVVy9SpyIGHHBzLnGvkog","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"• Incidencia: 11.4 x 1.000 días-catéter (Ramanan et al., 2015)(1)","guid":"wa4VCffIwR3IPpw-k_IQ0Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"17","parent":"0","text":"Microbiología","guid":"MrQqa4LDhKmkJvhwX7vMAw","children":[{"id":"18","parent":"17","text":"• Infecciones\\Nasociadas a DVE:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"• Monomicrobiana (57%):","guid":"XF0sEJlp2_c5i9KhCSHQyg","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"• Staphylococcus coagulasa (-): 63%","guid":"JfPBqg_XUqO4Vg4yABhD4g","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"• Propionibacterium acnes: 15%","guid":"N6yBRCL0l6N8TCqNbKSrxQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"19","text":"• Staphylococcus aureus: 11%","guid":"JJyQ36MgaZ0Cuz30icBShA","children":[]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"18","text":"• Polimicrobiana: 21%","guid":"4a9PSmgGh0th7p-iaJzpsQ","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"18","text":"• Cultivo negativo: 23%","guid":"moHNX3GTmXmXinGc5vlxPg","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"18","text":"• Fuente: Walti et al., 2013 (2)","guid":"CxJvq22CH1mJbx5ok-WWmQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"17","text":"• Infecciones asociadas\\Na shunt de LCR:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• Staphylococcus coagulasa (-): 37% (19% tempranas, 9% tardías)","guid":"f9SGUqu25VSMFtHa2JcLRw","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• Staphylococcus aureus: 18% (9% tempranas, 5% tardías)","guid":"w1hR2uRK5NG6QOupqOeK7A","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"26","text":"• Propionibacterium acnes: 9% (5% tempranas, 2% tardías)","guid":"guQi69pMuE4etPDCdSCTGw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"26","text":"• Polimicrobiana: 15%","guid":"7_7v5LKBjG2GTio_3HinVQ","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"26","text":"• Cultivo negativo: 9%","guid":"h2a92piD1YRj00JkcyqByg","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"26","text":"• Fuente: Conen et al., 2008 (3)","guid":"rfHCY-RX8J5pgHKKLIiG5g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"0","text":"Criterios Diagnósticos de Infección del\\NSistema Nervioso Central","guid":"ahxYxOsxFBMZc4SEOywW2w","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• Criterios\\Ndiagnósticos\\NCDC:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"• Microorganismo aislado en cultivo","guid":"tSC3FYRXSvO_cRg9RCYgSQ","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"• Síntomas\\Nclínicos:","guid":"dS3HyR51kyVj4rK-ktxPzw","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"• ≥2 síntomas sin otra causa en >1 año:","guid":"CCABZhTljbtyh8wZyrPm8g","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"• Fiebre >38°C","guid":"xHqrZ2Eqz9SfL0FU5_UdNA","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"• Cefalea","guid":"o7qK6wjTohgGLoFsmlrZ5w","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"36","text":"• Signos meníngeos","guid":"us7OcJ0peheSFOww4ARghw","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"36","text":"• Examen neurológico alterado","guid":"IXW8xn5UkHv8iInajKzrAQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"34","text":"• Hallazgos de\\Nlaboratorio:","guid":"f9R77ijzW7J10Mjhn2j2Dw","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"• Pleocitosis","guid":"hx3AMcTXuem7VVSEJ3VvSg","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"• Proteinorraquia","guid":"VXGhu5GrRv7wMDxdJuLH6Q","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"• Hipoglucorraquia","guid":"2NS_3xul_e8VF4uTLyzJdw","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"• Gram LCR (+)","guid":"xH-XWZw-jFAPbqZa12UN2w","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"42","text":"• Hemocultivo (+)","guid":"1XmeMjkM5ugAk7Nq38quKg","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"42","text":"• Otro método dg (+)","guid":"EbF7zcl9Xct0HupwYI2MLQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"0","text":"Manifestaciones Clínicas de\\NInfección DVE / DVP","guid":"oR_B7icOXErTbD3lNFGF_Q","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"• MO de poca virulencia \\N(≠ meningitis bacteriana):","guid":"XkBJh2tf2e7bAhRIFEAAGw","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"• Poca inflamación ⟶ posible ausencia de síntomas de meningitis","guid":"HN9eWYyugDpW3kqF-0s4Pw","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"• Presentación larvada","guid":"CwPxR42w1S9uzi9Yevv5kQ","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"50","text":"• Síntomas por HTIC ⟶ malfuncionamiento de la válvula (bloqueo mecánico por biofilm)","guid":"BIp5Phxt-HOMoA-xTFP1QQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"49","text":"• Síntomas\\Nprincipales:","guid":"3nPMCWzWjBq3k1NRFTgVqg","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"• Fiebre (>38°C) ⟶ 80%","guid":"nRqmgSPC80PEMWrkuOKWow","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• Al diagnóstico: 79% (p < 0.0001)","guid":"N1uyiZ2bS1A8d0f6W9tt1w","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"• Signos\\Nneurológicos:","guid":"IcxVo8GKBRu2EIEYGhRTsA","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Al diagnóstico: 31% (p = 0.003)","guid":"AXwvWR7E7NQmQPVoHVB31w","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"• Cefalea: 21%","guid":"hUOHvnuRceRj9lSH_lQpbA","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"• Cefalea, náuseas/vómitos","guid":"TmB_0Qm3R_2oZioq2gVQ9A","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"• Rigidez de nuca: 45%","guid":"MeN2ewP7Ao4M9_2gOKUGqg","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"57","text":"• Náuseas: 14%","guid":"Xz8OinX02Dbg2iUpRSdPfg","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"57","text":"• Disminución en GCS:\\N31%","guid":"XYUAqXl5whNt0BghbzhlCg","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"• Compromiso de conciencia ⟶ 20-65% (ausencia no descarta infección)","guid":"xFC1cWoCjmeNgcsI7odrdQ","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"•  7 puntos: 4% (p < 0.0001)","guid":"r7Vrqpger96XbcTzghayMw","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"63","text":"•  3 puntos: 15%","guid":"bkA6BdkqjeWyr0e83n66oQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"54","text":"• Signos\\Nlocales: 29%","guid":"-xhh41rF9H06GYo-JyyolA","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• Eritema: 19%","guid":"Qn3Ft6KVeJw7Aw9-32Ee3A","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"• Dolor: 15%","guid":"nvX0JAjVT11dZBSjgJ4FHA","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"• Secreción purulenta: 8%","guid":"TJx-jZwNHc4Ti6fqjKr9TA","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"54","text":"• Sin fiebre ni síntomas neurológicos o locales: 51%","guid":"Pf3D2Jx0Y2z85itV11VArA","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"49","text":"• Otros síntomas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"• Eritema o dolor en trayecto subcutáneo","guid":"9UxgdohvEmDgMai7QLwYTQ","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"• Dolor abdominal o signos de peritonitis (DVP), tendencia a formar pseudoquistes","guid":"lVJZFve43P2B-bQA8ux2oA","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"• Pleuritis (DV pleural)","guid":"6y_wLCwV1zziF0Ix7udifw","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"• Bacteriemia sin otra causa clara (DVA)","guid":"LclOWMQQbnKcP_pyN3rdog","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"72","text":"• Glomerulonefritis ⟶ 4-14% infecciones ventriculoatriales","guid":"62UERGpToxxrmVUyLG-4QA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"0","text":"Estudio LCR:\\NCitoquímico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"0","text":"Análisis LCR","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"• Alteraciones\\Ncitoquímicas:","guid":"UKBPEPpDzbrT_5HXQ9gEsw","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"• Recuento celular, glucosa, proteínas ⟶ No son indicadores confiables de infección.","guid":"EpGc1ufCWyjeh-EEe3wYhA","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"• Citoquímico normal ⟶ No excluye infección.","guid":"8oDg-8dcCyJMbBIkWdKp_A","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"• Tinción de Gram sin bacterias ⟶ No excluye infección, especialmente en pacientes tratados con antibióticos.","guid":"uivqD2g97YVvxASLM6LiFQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"79","text":"• Cultivo LCR:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"• Herramienta dg más relevante.","guid":"Cb2R74TELvcaXgCO0hn1Zg","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"• Si se sospecha infección y se retira el catéter ⟶ Cultivar catéter.","guid":"yDZEHFzhQrz5jPbCFW9L-w","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"84","text":"• NO hacer cultivo si no se sospecha infección.","guid":"uMvtFgLz39k6qs4mKkbM8g","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"84","text":"• Siempre cultivar antes de administrar antibióticos.","guid":"w8W6Abq7195i61EJN-Q0gw","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"84","text":"• Cultivo (-) con sospecha de infección:","guid":"QZvc6tBxwJwJEuHeLkoAQw","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"• Repetir y prolongar incubación a 10 días.","guid":"6oTAQ_Bb6658IKAVLYx1_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"84","text":"• Cultivo (+) sin contaminación:","guid":"qEBIBI1NLrknsKW2qgVEpw","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Si cultivo positivo para el mismo MO ⟶ Considerar infección verdadera.","guid":"e-_vzseHOtnugRjG-kP-GA","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"84","text":"• Cultivo (+) con sospecha de infección y\\N+/- alteraciones citoquímicas:","guid":"AfdYwDJfB8Fa2KZ9GFHVuQ","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"• Diagnóstico de\\Ninfección de DVE.","guid":"0Ip4Usj5MZ-VCkeVRRXuwA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"0","text":"Hemocultivos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"• Tomar hemocultivos en sospecha de infección de DVE.","guid":"VVEZGDa56qtc-ylUMTi5BQ","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"• Mejor rendimiento en DVA (>90%).","guid":"pjUtufI30GyrGdq-Q1gl1w","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"• En otras derivaciones ≈10%.","guid":"N7NsfHGYWOs9mK7q2Vds_Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"0","text":"PCR Universal","guid":"ABniiOrz4b6pMcKSvLUz6Q","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"• Técnica para la detección rápida de infecciones en LCR asociadas a shunt o ventriculostomía.","guid":"TMsmDWvCj4mSbUMXVbUubA","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"0","text":"Marcadores","guid":"","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"• LCR:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"• Lactato y Procalcitonina ⟶ Utilizados para diferenciación diagnóstica\\Nentre meningitis bacteriana post-neuroquirúrgica y meningitis aséptica.","guid":"v89LzIiatnDH0uYObzMLKQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"• β-D-glucano y Galactomanano ⟶ Evaluados como posibles marcadores.","guid":"dDau0CCy4CUR8kRY0VsiOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"• Séricos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• Procalcitonina sérica ⟶ Puede ayudar a diferenciar infección de postoperatorio.","guid":"2wDzLOjOPYmkH_L8ib7gZw","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"• Proteína C reactiva ⟶ Evaluada en la caracterización de infecciones asociadas a drenajes ventriculares.","guid":"dkEfW6vb6GD-VlkrEbLV_Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"0","text":"Imágenes","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"• Recomendado en sospecha de infección para evaluar obstrucción.","guid":"5ium8aXxVa5qOvfyMjAcTQ","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"• RNM con gadolinio ⟶ Método de elección.","guid":"1vGqf9Kid4XTvCUn12tm0A","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"• TAC de abdomen ⟶ Indicada en caso de DVP.","guid":"IZxXLswyBgFGBsJbvahuuQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento\\NEmpírico","guid":"ba8tcESksClEt87rJtxdLQ","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"• Esquema inicial:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"• Vancomicina + β-lactámico con\\Nactividad antipseudomónica:","guid":"j_sdY2N_BtwqVISTVBCLQQ","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"• Opciones: Cefepime, Ceftazidima, Meropenem","guid":"bbW4iez-a8L4MfErBA4HTg","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"• Elección según patrones de resistencia local.","guid":"0yTapn9CfG8k_GDnipJVJA","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"113","text":"• Ajustar según MO aislados previamente en el paciente.","guid":"nytAGabPmr_WqazGmHoO8w","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"112","text":"• Alternativas en\\Ncaso de alergia:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"• Anafilaxia a β-lactámicos: Aztreonam o Ciprofloxacino","guid":"J_-HRHNiZOCNIL7cn1C0YQ","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"• Mantener niveles de vancomicina entre 15-20 μg/mL.","guid":"UlxEUbQhjYLkgdi-vStS3Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento según\\NMicroorganismo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• SAMS:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"• Primera elección: Cloxacilina (NO cefazolina)","guid":"owBusfVNIviO4mO1SHQG2w","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"• Alternativa: Vancomicina","guid":"Rv7wciuwGKOirdIG99FO5Q","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"• Agregar Rifampicina si se mantiene el catéter.","guid":"Hwsn97Ed6uZmn_iDg4_BPg","children":[]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"121","text":"• SAMR:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"• Primera elección: Vancomicina (MIC <1)","guid":"iH8KiFKDJSoJi3kyaaBmjw","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"• Alternativas: Linezolid, Daptomicina, Cotrimoxazol","guid":"ivQCNGWZhDOq2Jmi0VZqgg","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"126","text":"• Agregar Rifampicina si se mantiene el catéter.","guid":"7NZYETki2sznvZu-Jve_KQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"130","parent":"121","text":"• Staph coagulasa (-): Igual esquema que para SAMS.","guid":"_mrn2ex1C6CiNlTfvAb7iA","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"121","text":"• Propionibacterium\\Nacnes:","guid":"faapVT1DkuvYnxhHnvIs0w","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"• Primera elección: Penicilina sódica","guid":"6xBVbM-x7s8NjeCGXo6MOA","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"• Alternativas: Vancomicina, Linezolid, Daptomicina, Ceftriaxona","guid":"03SgirsPvlmsbWsrMX4SNw","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"121","text":"• Gram (-):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"135","parent":"134","text":"• Enterobacterias:","guid":"hhKV_TgMZJAm40NNHgvk_g","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"• Primera elección: Ceftriaxona","guid":"ZOoUzYBPGdn5shEP8AgDiQ","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"• Alternativas: Meropenem, Aztreonam, BLEE","guid":"MzndSkNbC3RoZwAbm5ZYQg","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"134","text":"• Pseudomonas\\Naeruginosa:","guid":"TLRDmOMvFOHPDnUnZEjN_g","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"• Primera elección: Cefepime, Ceftazidima, Meropenem","guid":"gSMVhwiyZYCNAKQcWasrqQ","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"• Alternativas: Aztreonam, Ciprofloxacino","guid":"_2UaszA1JGQLfZ3aw4_U6A","children":[]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"134","text":"• Acinetobacter\\Nbaumannii:","guid":"dP18ZVMHra3RnfcXqmfNhQ","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"• Primera elección: Meropenem","guid":"v2tL3pJ6SEmUgFdx7qfBSQ","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"• Alternativa: Colistina","guid":"MJ-ud6cfXqI0rmWFWtqG_g","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento\\NIntraventricular","guid":"","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"• Indicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"• Pobre respuesta a antibióticos sistémicos (clínica o esterilización del LCR).","guid":"njbcSqdBPcg71LLp12WLGA","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"• MO multirresistentes sensibles solo a antibióticos con pobre penetración en SNC.","guid":"QU_4kzNKWdAtIZ-bP8H5bw","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"145","text":"• Imposibilidad de retirar el dispositivo.","guid":"HBLbRLgKDCxlscomXskd7A","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"144","text":"• Consideraciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"• Ningún ATB aprobado por la FDA para administración intratecal.","guid":"f2vB_joUSOu5thHCk9X1Gw","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"• Mayor experiencia con Vancomicina, Gentamicina y Colistina.","guid":"iKE_gXdwSS-Byc56EHDqbQ","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"149","text":"• Evitar PNC y Cefalosporinas por alta neurotoxicidad.","guid":"N7dxvUtKirHmOSC1FQDjNg","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"149","text":"• Al administrar ⟶ Lambpear por 15-60 min.","guid":"jfPOX-pXe3hn7Iemx98mrQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"154","parent":"0","text":"Duración del\\NTratamiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"• S. coagulasa (-) y P. acnes: 10-14 días.","guid":"bK6XD5SbzRefqqpqzbS8Vw","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"154","text":"• S. aureus o Gram (-): 10-14 días (puede extenderse a 21 días).","guid":"5BxnFUsBJ2oydxjaQC40Lw","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"154","text":"• Cultivos persistentemente positivos: Tratar por 10-14 días post cultivo negativo.","guid":"fvpQw1o0IznPlrYOzoX3hw","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"154","text":"• Imposibilidad de remover el dispositivo: Considerar terapia supresiva.","guid":"ZMGjTXQ3VMRoP5m_FPruCw","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"0","text":"Remoción\\Ndel Catéter","guid":"WwQzKY3FBOhQZWMr7-1NrQ","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"• Remoción del catéter (crucial por la formación de biofilm).","guid":"YAu4uSBGZCZiRvTgFDUDfQ","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"• Reinstalación una vez que el LCR esté estéril.","guid":"zKBrsAHROch67qi-1Rqjaw","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"0","text":"Seguimiento","guid":"","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"• Monitorización clínica es clave.","guid":"VfAFHibOopE0rZzozLM0VA","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"• En DVE, monitorizar con cultivos de LCR cada 48-72 hrs para asegurar esterilización.","guid":"jJALOxSmVshAFKJimxEa3Q","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"162","text":"• Evitar cultivos de rutina para buscar infección ⟶ Puede aumentar el riesgo de infección iatrogénica y es difícil de interpretar.","guid":"Tt6r7MGeazt-uA9JOZ--uA","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"0","text":"Conclusiones","guid":"","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"• Complicación grave y relativamente frecuente de estos dispositivos, generalmente causada por Gram (+) poco agresivos.","guid":"VaMa3uTVFR5uzpj0tBR6tA","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"• Diagnóstico\\Ndifícil:","guid":"FXrXs_e856Wleng4B766_A","children":[{"id":"169","parent":"168","text":"• Clínica inespecífica (fiebre lo más frecuente, alteraciones de conciencia en solo 1/3).","guid":"zg0_mAEn-2r7sc59t348PQ","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"168","text":"• Alteraciones del LCR variables (citoquímico puede ser normal).","guid":"4d1XaSiMyxnX514V_hjsOg","children":[]}]},{"id":"171","parent":"166","text":"• Pilares del tratamiento:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"• Retiro del catéter + antibióticos EV.","guid":"W-4powiX7cu719nWY1K0ng","children":[]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"166","text":"• Solo en ciertos casos requiere administración intraventricular.","guid":"Cw-VTDfTVT1s9yVjFpderA","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"166","text":"• Incluir Vancomicina y un β-lactámico con actividad antipseudomónica.","guid":"xJ73ReizGdeO2z5qO3H_CQ","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":174,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Infectología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Infectología","filename":"Infecciones de Dispositivos de Drenaje Ventricular-2024-1","id":"map_1144","resolved_references":[]}